### 网关地址（统一变量）
@gatewayHost = http://localhost:8080
@userServiceHost = http://localhost:8081

### 2. 通过网关注册（无需认证）
POST {{gatewayHost}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("TOKEN", response.body.data.token);
%}


### 3. 通过网关登录（无需认证）
# 登录后自动把 token 存到全局变量，后面直接用
POST {{gatewayHost}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("TOKEN", response.body.data.token);
%}


### 循环调用网关健康检查，测试负载均衡（轮询/随机）
### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 2
GET http://localhost:8081/health
### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 2
GET http://localhost:8082/health

### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 3
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/health

### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 4
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/health

### 测试网关负载均衡 - 请求 5
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/health